# Selector & POM Policy

**Canonical source:** [`docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md`](../../docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md)

When editing page objects or specs, follow the full policy including:

- Locator hierarchy (`getByRole` first)
- No locators in specs — use `@fixtures` page objects
- No assertions or manual sync in `src/pages/`
- Gate 1.1 audit checklist before commit

Do not duplicate rules here — read [`docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md`](../../docs/SELECTOR_POLICY.md).
